[FR::FR]#    HorizSync  30-64         # multisync
[FR::FR]#    HorizSync  31.5, 35.2    # multiple fixed sync frequencies
[FR::FR]#    HorizSync  15-25, 30-50  # multiple ranges of sync frequencies

